<i>that separated two Marines</i>
<i>from their pinned-down unit.</i>

16:00.461 --> 16:01.879
HERB: <i>Go three.</i>

16:01.962 --> 16:04.923
JERRY: <i>The mountains of the Hindu Kush</i>
<i>have been violent tribal areas</i>

16:05.049 --> 16:09.345
<i>since before Alexander the Great</i>
<i>marched through Persia on his way to India.</i>

16:09.428 --> 16:13.766
<i>On one dangerous night in March 2009,</i>
<i>two young Marines were on patrol...</i>

16:13.849 --> 16:16.810
<i>Intelligence they were gonna be smuggled</i>
<i>across the border by Pakistani Taliban.</i>

16:16.894 --> 16:19.480
<i>- And what else did the intelligence tell you?</i>
<i>- There was a ticking clock.</i>

16:19.563 --> 16:21.565
<i>We knew they were gonna be sold</i>
<i>for propaganda purposes.</i>

16:21.732 --> 16:23.233
<i>- Sold to al-Qaeda?</i>
<i>- Yes.</i>

16:23.317 --> 16:24.860
- SLOAN: <i>In a matter of days?</i>
<i>- Hours, really.</i>

16:24.943 --> 16:27.988
According to the Organization
