- Intern. Come on over.
- Yes?

23:28.241 --> 23:30.535
This is the overnight book.

23:30.619 --> 23:34.122
The night crew puts together every story
and every press release from everywhere.

23:34.206 --> 23:36.374
Go through this and separate
it into four piles,

23:36.458 --> 23:39.086
knew that, didn't know that,
don't care, and Shakira.

23:39.169 --> 23:41.338
- But that one's just for me, all right?
- MACKENZIE: Neal.

23:45.425 --> 23:46.760
- There's no statement yet.
- I know.

23:46.843 --> 23:48.178
It's the Pentagon.

23:48.261 --> 23:50.430
Is it possible they've responded
in a secret corner of the Internet?

23:50.514 --> 23:51.598
Secret corner of the Internet?

23:51.681 --> 23:54.226
Slay a dungeon wizard
to get the keys to Mordor or something?

23:54.351 --> 23:56.353
- It's not possible.
- Something that we need that Dumbledore...

23:56.478 --> 23:58.522
- Listen to yourself.
- I know, it's getting worse as I go on.

23:58.605 --> 24:00.482
- And it didn't start in a great place.
- Nothing in the book?

24:00.565 --> 24:01.650
Well, there are gonna be a ton of things

24:01.733 --> 24:02.776
in the book, but not from the Pentagon.

24:02.859 --> 24:04.486
I thought on the off chance
someone got a quote from them.

24:04.569 --> 24:06.404
- We'd know about it.
- Obviously I'm grasping at straws, Neal.

24:06.488 --> 24:07.739
There's no call to be patronizing.

24:08.615 --> 24:09.699
- You're right.
- Thank you.

24:09.783 --> 24:11.743
- Well, you're not, 'cause Mordor...
- I'm not the expert.

24:11.827 --> 24:12.786
You don't say.

24:12.869 --> 24:14.538
Do the book
and don't just farm it out to an intern.

24:14.621 --> 24:16.123
I'm delegating.

24:21.294 --> 24:23.296
- Fast Nationals?
- Right here.

24:23.380 --> 24:24.965
Just tell me if the number begins with a three.

24:25.340 --> 24:27.467
- It doesn't.
- 2.9?

24:27.551 --> 24:28.552
2.7?

24:28.927 --> 24:31.054
5.8 million viewers.

24:32.973 --> 24:34.641
- Shut the fuck up.
- That's gonna double

24:34.724 --> 24:37.060
when they add live-plus-same-day
and live-plus-seven.

24:37.144 --> 24:38.353
- Jesus Christ!
- Congratulations.

24:38.436 --> 24:40.021
Congratulations, man!

24:40.105 --> 24:41.773
Tracking looked good, but not like this.

24:41.857 --> 24:43.942
That's an <i>I Love Lucy</i> number.

24:44.025 --> 24:45.152
(LAUGHS)

