Yes.

24:47.779 --> 24:49.781
Yes. What?

24:49.865 --> 24:52.242
Don't worry about the call from Stomtonovich.

24:52.325 --> 24:53.451
I'm not.

24:53.535 --> 24:55.287
I am a little bit and I'll tell you why.

24:55.537 --> 24:58.206
