25:05.088 --> 25:07.507
He's thinking about the size of it
for the first time now.

25:07.591 --> 25:10.385
Yes. Yeah.

25:11.344 --> 25:12.637
The size of it.

25:13.763 --> 25:15.557
A new story creeping up on us?

25:15.640 --> 25:19.102
REBECCA: The morning of September 10.
The day after the broadcast.

25:19.186 --> 25:21.438
It was Neal's turn to do the overnight book,

25:21.521 --> 25:24.149
- but he staffed it out to an intern.
- Jenna Johnson.

